column5: Curious, I notice some of my posts are not published. Is this site edited?

[font color=green size=3][b]Moderators have been known to send offensive posts into cyberspace, however it's more likely that you are not doing something in the proper sequence. Wish'in I was fish'in on Wabby
Thank you. I'm too old to post scatological language, so I assume the error is on my end. On the other hand, if certain information is censored, overall content may lose the value of balance. Regards
